Silence of the Lambs" to seize the No. 1 position at the weekend box office.; 
  The sequel to last year's film about the exploits of four crime-fighting
turtles earned an impressive $20 million in its first weekend but played at
1,200 more screens than did "Silence," which grossed $6.7 million for second
place, Exhibitor Relations Co. Inc. reported Monday.  </LEADPARA>
